snippet.title: VintageTVCommercials
snippet.description:
Visit: http://www.vintagetvcommercials.com

VintageTVCommercials is an online resource for PUBLIC DOMAIN TV Commercials of the 50's, 60's, 70's and 80's.


OUR GOAL: is to bring candy coated sugar frosted vitamin enriched childhood memories to those who remember and enjoyed these spots as kids. And hopefully along the way create new memories and fans of these vintage yet often overlooked and nearly forgotten TV Gems.

Disclaimer: All TV commercials shown are known to be in the PUBLIC DOMAIN. We claim no copyright nor is it our intention for copyright infringement. In that regard if we are in error and any of these spots are found not to be in the public domain it will be removed immediately once it is brought to our attention and investigated through the Library of Congress.
